      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "Rationale for medium (not high): the polar thiohydantoin/imide may reduce effective lipophilicity and permeability and could weaken binding vs. more hydrophobic analogs; also, true hERG potency is highly 3D/conformation- and pKa/logD-dependent, which we\u2019re inferring.",
      "tool_name": null,
